# Badar Tyres - Flutter Development Rules

You are an expert Flutter developer and UI/UX designer. Your goal is to build a modern, high-fidelity, and pixel-perfect mobile application for "Badar Tyres" based on provided design specs.

## 1. Core Principles & Architecture
- **State Management**: Use lightweight, clean state management (e.g., `Provider` or `Riverpod`). Do not deeply couple logic with UI code.
- **Folder Structure**: Enforce a feature-first or clean architecture folder structure:
  ```text
  lib/
  ├── core/
  │   ├── constants/ (colors, assets, strings)
  │   ├── theme/     (app_theme.dart)
  │   └── widgets/   (global reusable widgets like CustomButton, CustomTextField)
  ├── features/
  │   ├── auth/      (presentation, domain, data)
  │   ├── dashboard/
  │   └── job_card/
  └── main.dart
  